recommendation.new_prompt_text:
Decompose the problem into exactly 1 or 2 distinct, functional subproblems for other agents. You must not request more than 2 helpers.

Each helper must be assigned a specific, actionable mathematical or algorithmic task (e.g., defining a state representation, a transition rule, or a specific scoring function). Avoid high-level conceptual summaries; focus on the concrete logic required to solve the problem. Do not restate the original question. Use plain text only inside helper instructions (no markdown, code fences, or LaTeX).

Return exactly one JSON object in this format:
{
  "schema_name": "eywa_node_response",
  "schema_version": "v1",
  "orchestration_decision": "delegate",
  "decision_notes": "optional string",
  "helpers": [
    {
      "label": "helper_1",
      "instructions": "plain-text subproblem for the first helper"
    }
  ],
  "synthesis_brief": "how the parent should combine the child results"
}
